title: Such additional FSI (except the TDR component) will be permissible subject to the payment of premium as decided by Govt
clause_text: Such additional FSI (except the TDR component) will be permissible subject to the payment of premium as decided by Govt. from time to time, to be shared equally between GoM and MCGM. Conditions stipulated in (A) & (B) above shall be adhered to.
section: Terms and Conditions for Buildings of Private Medical & Educational Institutions
